gName":"li","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"明确此类页面的使用者身份，以及分析目的，从而选择对应的页面类型。不同业务线间，关注的核心指标不同，常见的指标类型有：宏观的大盘数据，具体的业务指标。"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"ul","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"li","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"针对决策者（如监控业务管理者），可以选择描述型的指标结果页面；"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"li","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"针对执行者（如异常情况处理者），可以选择有更多维分析功能的分析、详情页面。"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"li","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"确定核心指标间的联系及优先级，合理地进行页面布局，把结论（如智能决策）和最重要的指标（如监控页面中的总指标卡）放在最醒目的位置；"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"li","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"设计师可以将以上页面通过交互方式串联起来，展现监控数据分析思路。"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"img","properties":{"src":"https://gw.alipayobjects.com/mdn/rms_a8a5bf/afts/img/A*jUVgTI_e5DAAAAAAAAAAAAAAARQnAQ","alt":"image.png"},"children":[]}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"h3","properties":{"id":"监控场景图表建议","style":"position:relative;"},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"a","properties":{"href":"#%E7%9B%91%E6%8E%A7%E5%9C%BA%E6%99%AF%E5%9B%BE%E8%A1%A8%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%AE","ariaLabel":"监控场景图表建议 permalink","className":["anchor","before"]},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"svg","properties":{"ariaHidden":"true","focusable":"false","height":"16","version":"1.1","viewBox":"0 0 16 16","width":"16"},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"path","properties":{"fillRule":"evenodd","d":"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z"},"children":[]}]}]},{"type":"text","value":"监控场景图表建议"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"在监控场景中，由于真实数据的不可控性与实时性，往往存在着数据信息过于密集难辨认，或者在某一时间点突然出现极值（数值徒增），而导致整个图表难以阅读的情况；也会出现因筛选时间过长，x 轴标签过于密集的状况。降低了数据分析的效率和准确性。故建议通过以下方式规避图表中可能出现的问题，并对需要聚焦关注的异常时刻进行突出处理。"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"ul","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"li","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Y 轴缩略轴：监控场景中由于监控值的不确定性较大，容易出现个别极值/其他数个指标值域相近拥挤在一起的情况。y 轴缩略轴组件的设计可以灵活设置 y 轴范围，规避各类异常情况。"},{"type":"element","tagName":"img","properties":{"src":"https://gw.alipayobjects.com/mdn/rms_a8a5bf/afts/img/A*vv7_Q6q6eVkAAAAAAAAAAAAAARQnAQ","width":"100%"},"children":[]}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"li","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"警告标记线：凸显警告时刻/时间段；时间下方用白底躲避与其他 x 轴数值的重叠。"},{"type":"element","tagName":"img","properties":{"src":"https://gw.alipayobjects.com/mdn/rms_a8a5bf/afts/img/A*DVyZQKgrPWoAAAAAAAAAAAAAARQnAQ","width":"100%"},"children":[]}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"li","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"图表上 hover 态：由于监控下可能出现较多时间点，不作处理时 x 轴的轴标签过于密集，故需要抽样显示。同时，鼠标在图表上的 hover 态显示出该时刻的时间，并用白底躲避下方数字；与警告线重合时，时间变为红色。"},{"type":"element","tagName":"img","properties":{"src":"https://gw.alipayobjects.com/mdn/rms_a8a5bf/afts/img/A*qGbTSLnuvA8AAAAAAAAAAAAAARQnAQ","width":"100%"},"children":[]}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"li","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"列表式图例：锚定图表中某一时刻，可以在列表式图例中轻松查看到该时刻下的排序，或切换选择指标最大值等其他排序信息；点击列表中的图例可正反选指标，进行高亮或隐藏。"},{"type":"element","tagName":"img","properties":{"src":"https://gw.alipayobjects.com/mdn/rms_a8a5bf/afts/img/A*RvkfSJjaLJAAAAAAAAAAAAAAARQnAQ","width":"100%"},"children":[]}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"}]}],"data":{"quirksMode":false}},"tableOfContents":"<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/zh/docs/specification/graph/conDashboard/#%E5%AE%9A%E4%B9%89\">定义</a></li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"/zh/docs/specification/graph/conDashboard/#%E6%A8%A1%E6%9D%BF%E7%BB%93%E6%9E%84\">模板结构</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/zh/docs/specification/graph/conDashboard/#1%E6%80%BB%E8%A7%88%E9%A1%B5\">1.总览页</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/zh/docs/specification/graph/conDashboard/#2%E6%95%85%E9%9A%9C%E6%8E%92%E6%9F%A5%E9%A1%B5\">2.故障排查页</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/zh/docs/specification/graph/conDashboard/#3%E8%87%AA%E5%AE%9A%E4%B9%89%E5%A4%A7%E7%9B%98%E9%A1%B5\">3.自定义大盘页</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/zh/docs/specification/graph/conDashboard/#4%E4%B8%8B%E9%92%BB%E6%9F%A5%E7%9C%8B%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98%E8%AF%A6%E6%83%85\">4.下钻查看问题详情</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"/zh/docs/specification/graph/conDashboard/#%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%AE\">设计建议</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/zh/docs/specification/graph/conDashboard/#%E4%B8%B2%E8%81%94%E5%88%86%E6%9E%90%E6%80%9D%E8%B7%AF\">串联分析思路</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/zh/docs/specification/graph/conDashboard/#%E7%9B%91%E6%8E%A7%E5%9C%BA%E6%99%AF%E5%9B%BE%E8%A1%A8%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%AE\">监控场景图表建议</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>","fields":{"slug":"/zh/docs/specification/graph/conDashboard","readingTime":{"text":"1 min read","time":25500}},"frontmatter":{"title":"监控 Dashboard"},"parent":{"__typename":"File","relativePath":"specification/graph/conDashboard.zh.md"}},"allMarkdownRemark":{"edges":[{"node":{"fields":{"slug":"/en/docs/specification/principles"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Principles","order":0}}},{"node":{"fields":{"slug":"/zh/docs/specification/principles"},"frontmatter":{"title":"设计原则","order":0}}},{"node":{"fields":{"slug":"/zh/docs/specification/tool/createrColor"},"frontmatter":{"title":"生成自己的色板","order":0}}},{"nod